{"TopicId":148792,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Time Freeze feature","CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T19:37:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T19:37:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne thing this game really needs is a feature that allows us to slow down, or stop time, that is REAL time. \u00A0 That way I may actually get some to play it enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen I can fire up my PC for (what my wife sees as) half an hour, but I can get a good four hours or more at a stretch without neglecting my chores or feeling guilty.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know Squad can work miracles, \u00A0they proved it with\u00A01.2, so they should be able to knock this out in time for the full release.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and if you can do it so I don\u0027t age whilst in time freeze that would be a really cool added bonus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Magzimum","CreatedById":167187,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T07:39:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea. I\u0027d like to play for 32 hours every day as well. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T20:40:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least a \u0022pause time\u0022 feature. Great if you need to select something with the moving parts and menus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T09:44:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778469\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475095256\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103726\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZooNamedGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, ZooNamedGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least a \u0022pause time\u0022 feature. Great if you need to select something with the moving parts and menus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a bad idea, but I suspect you didn\u0027t study the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E very deeply\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T09:59:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222779262\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475142281\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a bad idea, but I suspect you didn\u0027t study the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E very deeply\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI sorta did XD .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T12:49:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also think this forum needs more humorous suggestions. This one is gold XD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222776823\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475005059\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 27/09/2016 at 4:37 PM, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(...)I can fire up my PC for (what my wife sees as) half an hour(...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMine has a spider sense for KSP. It\u0027s like, I hadn\u0027t played for over a month, 1.2 comes out and I fire it up, and just when I see the loading bar creeping up right\u00A0near completion, I can hear her getting up from her computer chair and coming my way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022You\u0027re ALWAYS playing this game!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShe also complains I\u0027m always installing mods and building rockets, and never flying\u00A0anything.\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EShe\u0027s right, there.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Blaarkies","CreatedById":153700,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T14:31:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778469\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475095256\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103726\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZooNamedGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, ZooNamedGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least a \u0022pause time\u0022 feature. Great if you need to select something with the moving parts and menus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike a spaceplane tumbling out of control, while you are trying to right-click the correct two fuel tanks and transfer some weight...pause would really save us there \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T14:35:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222779559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475159469\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153700\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Blaarkies\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Blaarkies said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike a spaceplane tumbling out of control, while you are trying to right-click the correct two fuel tanks and transfer some weight...pause would really save us there \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve found the Locked Camera is a major boon in\u00A0those situations (well, I don\u0027t fly planes, but finding the right part to right-click during tumbles anyway). Besides, seeing the horizon/skybox spinning out of control like that scene on Gravity is such an adrenaline rush XD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}